George and the Printer is a fun and challenging puzzle game where you will help George overcome funny situations in his journey to solve printer problems. With this Chrome extension, you can easily play games right in your browser without needing to install additional software.

In the game, George has to deal with a broken printer and troubles related to printing. You'll need to find creative ways to repair printers, solve related problems, and complete printing tasks as quickly as possible, avoiding delays and getting George in trouble.
